Author: ruzuki
Text: I had to unsubscribe from every delivery/fast food related email list. I signed up for a ton of lists last year around my birthday for free food. But I just cant handle them sending me deals every week... Thrifty brain is like "But you'll save money if you eat it now instead of when its not on sale!" and I have to remember "Ill save more money, AND lose weight, if I eat it never".
